### Проект 2 (5.6 — Material.Avalonia)

Создай **отдельный новый проект**, добавь пакет:
```bash
dotnet add package Material.Avalonia
```

**App.axaml**
```xml
<Application xmlns="https://github.com/avaloniaui"
             xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml"
             xmlns:themes="clr-namespace:Material.Styles.Themes;assembly=Material.Styles"
             x:Class="AvaloniaMaterial.App"
             RequestedThemeVariant="Light">

    <Application.Styles>
        <themes:MaterialTheme BaseTheme="Light" 
                              PrimaryColor="Purple" 
                              SecondaryColor="Lime"/>
    </Application.Styles>
</Application>
```

**MainWindow.axaml** (просто пример)
```xml
<Window ... Title="Material Avalonia">
    <StackPanel Margin="30" Spacing="20">
        <TextBlock Text="Material Avalonia Example" FontSize="18" FontWeight="Bold"/>
        <TextBox Text="Обычный TextBox"/>
        <TextBox Text="Outlined" UseFloatingWatermark="True" Classes="outline dense"/>
        <Button Content="Material Button"/>
    </StackPanel>
</Window>
```

